-- American Home Mortgage plunges 87 pct
-- 
-- Tue Jul 31, 2007 2:25pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/31/us-markets-stocks-americanhome-idUSN3144388620070731

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of American Home Mortgage Investment Corp. AHM.N resumed trading on Tuesday, plunging 87 percent after the mortgage lender said it is unable to fund home loans and may have to liquidate its assets. 

 Shares of American Home were halted before the bell on Monday after closing at $10.47 on the New York Stock Exchange on Friday. They were trading at $1.40 on Tuesday.